    # fn "「...Ju-Ju-Juuichi-san!{p} You got to the point so suddenly!」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_s_02.ks (KS 596-597)
    fn "「……柔[wdt]柔[wdt]柔[wdt]柔一！[l]一下就讲到这里也太突然了！」"

# game/day 12.rpy:794
translate chinese_simplified juuichi12_stick_5362de03:

    # "I can't help but comment.{p}He's being a little too hasty, isn't he?!{p}Some things have to be set up first!"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_s_02.ks (KS 599-601)
    "我一不小心就插嘴了。[l]这是不是有点太性急了啊！[l]不管什么事，[wdt]都应该要循序渐进地来不是吗！"

# game/day 12.rpy:798
translate chinese_simplified juuichi12_stick_bde1762b:

    # ju "「...?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_s_02.ks (KS 606)
    ju "「……？」"

# game/day 12.rpy:799
translate chinese_simplified juuichi12_stick_dc8c8e67:

    # "He looks at me, confused."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_s_02.ks (KS 608-610)
    "你在说什么啊。[l]柔一现在脸上的表情要说是什么意思的话，[wdt]应该是这样没错吧。"

# game/day 12.rpy:800
translate chinese_simplified juuichi12_stick_c3871193:

    # "But I'm the one that's confused here!{p}I take my eyes off Juuichi-san,\nand look back over to Soutarou-kun."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_s_02.ks (KS 612-614)
    "不过想要这么说的应该是我才对吧！[l]然而我的心声却被简单地无视了。[l]柔一不再看我，[wdt]转头回去继续对宗太郎说道。"

# game/day 12.rpy:804
translate chinese_simplified juuichi12_stick_16acab3d:

    # ju "「Be careful not to overdo it.{p} Excessive training will hinder your growth.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_s_02.ks (KS 619-620)
    ju "「过度的锻鍊是不行的。[l]反而会妨碍身体的成长。」"

# game/day 12.rpy:805
translate chinese_simplified juuichi12_stick_7dc1072f:

    # so "「Got it...」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_s_02.ks (KS 623)
    so "「知道了的……」"

# game/day 12.rpy:810
translate chinese_simplified juuichi12_stick_70483e39:

    # fn "「No, no, it doesn't get bigger from muscle training!{p} Don't you mean blood?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_s_02.ks (KS 629-630)
    fn "「不不，那里不是肌肉所以没办法练大的！[l]应该是血液比较多还是什么的。」"

# game/day 12.rpy:811
translate chinese_simplified juuichi12_stick_07e8fa1f:

    # "I interrupt Soutarou-kun without meaning to."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_s_02.ks (KS 632-633)
    "我的喊声把宗太郎说的话打断了。[l]结果还是情不自禁地插嘴了。"

# game/day 12.rpy:817
translate chinese_simplified juuichi12_stick_9491de8a:

    # "Maybe Juuichi-san is uninformed about these things?{p}I thought he'd be a more knowledgeable about this,\nso I'm kind of surprised."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_s_02.ks (KS 640-642)
    "柔一该不会对那方面没什么了解吧。[l]因为感觉他对这种事情应该也很清楚，稍微有点意外。"

# game/day 12.rpy:818
translate chinese_simplified juuichi12_stick_7e39d124:

    # "...Should I lend a hand?{p}I decide to so."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_s_02.ks (KS 644-645)
    "总而言之……这里也只能让我来尽力帮忙了。[l]偷偷地下了这样的决心。"

# game/day 12.rpy:819
translate chinese_simplified juuichi12_stick_49fa229b:

    # "How to start...?{p}First, I'll ask him what his type is...{w=.2} No!"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_s_02.ks (KS 647-648)
    "一开始要先教什么好呢……[l]还是先问问宗太郎喜欢的类型……[wdt]不对啦！"

# game/day 12.rpy:820
translate chinese_simplified juuichi12_stick_bf11728f:

    # "Theories as to why ejaculation occurs?{w=.2}\nAll right, [fn]-sensei's impromptu\nhealth lesson begins now!"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_s_02.ks (KS 650-656)
    "还是先照理论来说，为什么会发生射精这种现象，[wdt]从这里开始比较好吧。[se 鉄パイプ]好，[wdt]博行老师的小型健康教育课程，[wdt]现在开始！"

# game/day 12.rpy:824
translate chinese_simplified juuichi12_stick_5f233a8a:

    # "...The two of them have been giving me\na strange look this whole time.{w=.2}\nMaybe I didn't phrase it right?"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_s_02.ks (KS 658-660)
    "……怎么着，[wdt]从刚刚开始两人看我的眼神，好像微妙地有种鄙视感。[l]现在可能不要开口反而是正解也不一定。"

# game/day 12.rpy:825
translate chinese_simplified juuichi12_stick_ccdf8c61:

    # ju "「[ln],{w=.2} what are you talking about?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_s_02.ks (KS 663)
    ju "「西村，[wdt]你从刚刚开始到底在说什么？」"

# game/day 12.rpy:826
translate chinese_simplified juuichi12_stick_b8fadfe5:

    # fn "「You know...{w} We're talking about 'that', right?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_s_02.ks (KS 666)
    fn "「所以说，[l]……不是在说那个的话题吗？」"

# game/day 12.rpy:827
translate chinese_simplified juuichi12_stick_54dcc393:

    # so "「What do you mean, 'that'?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_s_02.ks (KS 669)
    so "「那个？[l] 那个到底是什么的说？」"

# game/day 12.rpy:828
translate chinese_simplified juuichi12_stick_8c5d35ba:

    # "I'm on the verge of tears.{p}Soutarou-kun, your big brother\ndoesn't like it when you play dumb."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_s_02.ks (KS 671-673)
    "我觉得有点想哭。[l]宗太郎同学，[wdt]自己的话题还丢在一旁假装不知道什么的哥哥可一点都不会觉得感激喔。"

# game/day 12.rpy:829
translate chinese_simplified juuichi12_stick_54e8e22b:

    # "...What is this?{w} Are they teasing me?{p}Did I become a joke character without realizing?"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_s_02.ks (KS 675-676)
    "……该不会是那个吧？[l] 在欺负刚加入话题的我？[l]我是什么时候变成这种被虐狂角色啦。"

# game/day 12.rpy:830
translate chinese_simplified juuichi12_stick_a69db6d5:

    # fn "「{size=-10}You know,{w=.2} that thing. {size=+10}」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_s_02.ks (KS 679)
    fn "「[fsma]所以说，[wdt]那个就是那个嘛，[fdef]」"

# game/day 12.rpy:831
translate chinese_simplified juuichi12_stick_76524e44:

    # "I look down,{w=.2}\ntowards the area of Juuichi-san's\nand Soutarou-kun's"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_s_02.ks (KS 681-682)
    "我别开视线，[wdt]低头往下看。[l]差不多就是看向柔一和宗太郎的那里的高度。"

# game/day 12.rpy:832
translate chinese_simplified juuichi12_stick_9c5643c2:

    # "...But they still don't get it?{p}They ask again."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_s_02.ks (KS 684-685)
    "……不过，[wdt]他们似乎没注意到我的意图，再次向我问道。"

# game/day 12.rpy:836
translate chinese_simplified juuichi12_stick_6ca31f83:

    # so "「[ln]-senpai,{w=.2} I don't understand.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_s_02.ks (KS 690)
    so "「西村学长，[wdt]这样听不懂的说。」"

# game/day 12.rpy:840
translate chinese_simplified juuichi12_stick_9499b134:

    # ju "「You're a man, say what's on your mind.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_s_02.ks (KS 695)
    ju "「是男人的话就爽快地说出来。」"

# game/day 12.rpy:842
translate chinese_simplified juuichi12_stick_365034c3:

    # "...{p}...{p}..."
    ""

# game/day 12.rpy:846
translate chinese_simplified juuichi12_stick_a74bd440:

    # "Pop.{p}I'm pretty sure something just burst inside me."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_s_02.ks (KS 703-704)
    "啪叽。[l]我听到，[wdt]自己心中有某种东西断掉的声音。"

# game/day 12.rpy:851
translate chinese_simplified juuichi12_stick_771ade42:

    # fn "{size=+15}「You know,{w=.2} that thing all men\n have dangling from their crotches!」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_s_02.ks (KS 710-711)
    fn "「[fbig]所以说，[wdt]只要是男人谁都会在意悬挂在两腿间的东西不是吗！！[fdef]」"

# game/day 12.rpy:856
translate chinese_simplified juuichi12_stick_79a69f06:

    # "I say it all at once.{p}{nw}"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_s_02.ks (KS 721)
    "一口气把话讲出来了。[l][se 夢]"

# game/day 12.rpy:858
translate chinese_simplified juuichi12_stick_697d4323:

    # extend "Wow, that was a liberating feeling...!"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_s_02.ks (KS 722)
    extend "啊啊，[wdt]该怎么说才好呢，这个开放感……！"

# game/day 12.rpy:859
translate chinese_simplified juuichi12_stick_1bccc5f8:

    # "It was like...{p}Leaving footprints on fresh snow.{p}I said it.{w=.2} I said it!!"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_s_02.ks (KS 724-726)
    "简直像……对。[l]在刚下完的雪上踩出足迹，[wdt]那种感觉。[l]我说出来了。[wdt]说出来了啊！！"

# game/day 12.rpy:860
translate chinese_simplified juuichi12_stick_1960ca55:

    # "I get the urge to cry out in joy,{w=.2}\nbut I suppress the feeling."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_s_02.ks (KS 728-729)
    "虽然有种想要马上大喊「呀呼――」的衝动，[wdt]不过因为这里不是山上所以先按捺住了。"

# game/day 12.rpy:861
translate chinese_simplified juuichi12_stick_75fdb88f:

    # "...Then,{w=.2} I take a look the two of them."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_s_02.ks (KS 731)
    "……那么，[wdt]看看听到这些话的人反应如何吧。"

# game/day 12.rpy:867
translate chinese_simplified juuichi12_stick_01ece481:

    # "Soutarou-kun looks completely bewildered,{w=.2}\nand Juuichi-san looks flabbergasted.{p}Huh? This isn't the reaction I was expecting..."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_s_02.ks (KS 738-740)
    "宗太郎是一脸的困惑，[wdt]柔一则是满脸茫然的表情。[l]哎呀哎呀，[wdt]怎么跟我想像的反应不一样？"

# game/day 12.rpy:868
translate chinese_simplified juuichi12_stick_a109940d:

    # ju "「I was talking about weight training...」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_s_02.ks (KS 743)
    ju "「我在说的，[wdt]是重训的话题……」"

# game/day 12.rpy:869
translate chinese_simplified juuichi12_stick_e306754d:

    # so "「Uh, me too...」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_s_02.ks (KS 746)
    so "「我，[wdt]我也是在说这个的说……」"

# game/day 12.rpy:870
translate chinese_simplified juuichi12_stick_00b00233:

    # fn "「...」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_s_02.ks (KS 749)
    fn "「……」"

