translate chinese_simplified juuichi12_stick_6905ef53:

    # so "「...」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_s_02.ks (KS 755)
    so "「……」"

# game/day 12.rpy:876
translate chinese_simplified juuichi12_stick_5191ce4a:

    # "A terrible silence falls upon us.{p}Even the cicadas pick up on the mood,{w=.2}\nand stop their incessant noise."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_s_02.ks (KS 759-761)
    "简直可以用恐怖来形容的沉默，[wdt]突然笼罩住了我们。[l]彷彿会读气氛似的，[wdt]四周的蝉鸣声也突然停了下来。"

# game/day 12.rpy:877
translate chinese_simplified juuichi12_stick_41048fcf:

    # "In an instant, all my blood rushes to my face.{p}You could fry an egg on it at the moment."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_s_02.ks (KS 763-764)
    "一瞬间血都衝到了脸上。[l]现在我的脸应该烫到可以煎荷包蛋了吧。"

# game/day 12.rpy:878
translate chinese_simplified juuichi12_stick_47b29a7b:

    # so "「...S-senpai...」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_s_02.ks (KS 767)
    so "「……学，[wdt]学长，」"

# game/day 12.rpy:879
translate chinese_simplified juuichi12_stick_14a23075:

    # fn "「...Hm?{w=.2} What is it, Soutarou-kun?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_s_02.ks (KS 770)
    fn "「……嗯，怎么了吗宗太郎同学？」"

# game/day 12.rpy:880
translate chinese_simplified juuichi12_stick_6d98c32d:

    # "Is he trying to cover for me or something?"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_s_02.ks (KS 772-773)
    "像是要跟上什么似的，[wdt]宗太郎对我说道。"

# game/day 12.rpy:881
translate chinese_simplified juuichi12_stick_d0bf3fb0:

    # "When he sees my face, though,{w=.2}\nhe groans and says no more."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_s_02.ks (KS 775-776)
    "可是当他一看到我的脸，[wdt]就呜的一声然后沉默了下来。"

# game/day 12.rpy:882
translate chinese_simplified juuichi12_stick_ab310180:

    # "I guess I've made quite the facial expression.{p}I suppose it doesn't matter any more."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_s_02.ks (KS 778-779)
    "我现在应该是一脸半死不活的表情吧。[l]嗯，[wdt]不过那种事怎样都好了啦。"

# game/day 12.rpy:886
translate chinese_simplified juuichi12_stick_11a7ea0f:

    # "I slowly step backwards, heading towards home."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_s_02.ks (KS 783)
    "我拖着脚步，[wdt]慢慢地，[wdt]往家的方向走去。"

# game/day 12.rpy:890
translate chinese_simplified juuichi12_stick_07a61325:

    # "Then I turn around and run.{p}Like the wind."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_s_02.ks (KS 787)
    "[wdss]就连　稍微　回头看　也没有"

# game/day 12.rpy:906
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_51c9ea41:

    # fn "「White clouds, blue sky,\n and cicada noises, way off in the distance.{p} Today is another peaceful day in Minasato Village.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 18-19)
    fn "「白色的云，[l]蓝色的天空，[l]远处传来蝉鸣的声音。[l]今天的水乡村也是一如既往的平和[wdt]啊。」"

# game/day 12.rpy:907
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_cbd28ad5:

    # "Alone at the grounds, I monologued to myself."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 21)
    "谁都不在的院内，一个人对着风嘟囔着。"

# game/day 12.rpy:908
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_6e4561af:

    # "No reason in particular.{p}Not even a tiny bit of purpose."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 23)
    "完全没有意义啊。[l]连1厘米的意义都没啊。[l]"

# game/day 12.rpy:909
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_4469e095:

    # "There are some things that I feel like doing,\nso I just do them."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 24)
    "只是觉得想那样做，于是就那样做了。"

# game/day 12.rpy:910
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_5584018d:

    # "Nevertheless, my words themselves are true.{p}Today, Minasato is the same as it always was.{p}The breeze in my face felt so refreshing."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 26-28)
    "不过，说出来的内容的确是事实。[l]今天的水乡村也是老样子。[l]面前吹过的风让人感到极度的清爽。"

# game/day 12.rpy:911
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_4de8401d:

    # "Yep,{w=.2} very elegant."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 30)
    "嗯，[wdt]十分风雅。"

# game/day 12.rpy:912
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_0e556978:

    # ka "「Well, if it isn't [fn].」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 35)
    ka "「哦，这不是博行嘛。」"

# game/day 12.rpy:916
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_5fd6f655:

    # "While looking at the dreamily swinging branches,\na voice reached my ears."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 38-39)
    "当朦胧地望着摇曳的树枝时，那样的招呼声传到了我的耳朵里。"

# game/day 12.rpy:920
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_53f8e64d:

    # "When I looked over, Kouya's form coming up\nthe stone steps reflected in my eyes."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 43-44)
    "将视线转移，石阶的对面映出洸哉的身姿。"

# game/day 12.rpy:921
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_535bbda2:

    # fn "「Huh, what's going on, Kouya?\nDidn't expect to see you here.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 47-48)
    fn "「咦，怎么了吗洸哉。来这种地方？」"

# game/day 12.rpy:925
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_3b6a1a03:

    # ka "「I could ask you the same thing.{p} What are you doing, here at a Shinto shrine?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 53-54)
    ka "「我才要问你呢。[l]你跑到神社这种地方干什么。」"

# game/day 12.rpy:926
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_f66b9ec9:

    # fn "「...Nothing much, just killing time.{p} I don't have anything to do, really.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 57-58)
    fn "「……没什么，只是打发时间。[l]没什么要做的事。」"

# game/day 12.rpy:927
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_7283c4fc:

    # "Ever since I got back to Minasato,\nI've been getting the feeling\nthat most days are like this."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 60-61)
    "话说回来，自从回到水乡村以后，不知怎么的日子好像都是这样子的。"

# game/day 12.rpy:928
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_60ab5825:

    # "Everyone else is also on vacation,\nbut it's not like their days are free.{p}They might have clubs, work, or household helping."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 63-64)
    "虽然是暑假，大家却也不是每天都有空闲的。[l]有的有社团活动，有的要打工，有的要帮忙家里的工作。"

# game/day 12.rpy:929
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_1850f124:

    # "Therefore, they don't have much time to be alone."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 66)
    "所以，只有1个人的时候并不少见。"

# game/day 12.rpy:930
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_5685ca9c:

    # "When that itself becomes a way of having leisure,\nI don't really hate it,{p}but I can't help but feel a bit sad."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 68-70)
    "只有自己本身悠闲自在的，虽然不讨厌这样子，[l]但是帮不上什么忙还是有点让人悲伤的。"

# game/day 12.rpy:931
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_4a4e664d:

    # "And this method of killing time\nwas just a spontaneous attempt at something,\nso maybe something new might happen."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 72-74)
    "为了打发时间，我就这样眺望着自然的风景，结果反而更闲了。"

# game/day 12.rpy:935
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_ea270a40:

    # ka "「Ahh...{w} sorry.{p} You just came back, but I haven't had much time.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 79-80)
    ka "「呃……[l]抱歉呐。[l]难得你能回来，却没什么时间陪你。」"

# game/day 12.rpy:936
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_01b2ba53:

    # fn "「Nah, don't apologize.{p} You didn't do anything wrong, Kouya.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 83-84)
    fn "「不不，不用道歉啦。[l]这又不是洸哉的错。[l]"

# game/day 12.rpy:937
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_866937fb:

    # fn "「Besides, something like this is a bit nostalgic,\n so I don't mind.{w} Anyway, what brings you here?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 85-88)
    fn "而且说起来，这种怀念的感觉并不令人讨厌啊。」「那么，洸哉到这里来做什么呢？」"

# game/day 12.rpy:941
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_d55addd9:

    # ka "「Hmm, if I had to sum it up, I'm here to guide.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 93)
    ka "「嗯，硬要说的话，是来做向导的。」"

# game/day 12.rpy:942
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_d68169e2:

    # fn "「Guide?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 96)
    fn "「向导？」"

# game/day 12.rpy:943
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_e50c16d4:

    # "I don't really get that."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 98)
    "刚才那句话我不是很明白。"

# game/day 12.rpy:944
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_96ca0201:

    # "「What do you mean?」 I was about to ask.{p}But before it could get out, the words\nwere erased by another voice calling out."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 100-102)
    "本来想再问「那是怎么回事」的我。[l]在发出那个声音前，就被别的声音所淹没了。"

# game/day 12.rpy:945
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_d518da9c:

    # who "「Heeey, Kouyaa~.{w} Big Brother is kinda old here,\n so ease up on the heavy exercise.{p} Anyway, wait a sec,{nw}"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 105-107)
    who "「喂～洸哉～[l]大哥我年纪大了，不适合做那么剧烈的运动啦。[l]所以给我等一下啦，[se play=\"bosu35\"][qxv]喂」[wqx]"

# game/day 12.rpy:948
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_6a9ab346:

    # extend " damn it.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 107)
    extend "所以给我等一下啦，[se play=\"bosu35\"][qxv]喂」[wqx]"

# game/day 12.rpy:949
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_cb35faa8:

    # "The words being spoken didn't seem that tired,\nbut rather bright.{w} From the stone steps\nwere three people that I'd never seen before."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 109-110)
    "从话语中完全感觉不到疲惫的，洪亮的声音。[l]往石阶的方向瞥了一眼，是从未见过的三人组合。"

# game/day 12.rpy:957
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_b151e9a1:

    # "A light brown-haired horseman,{p}a clear-eyed birdman,{p}and a short-statured tricolored catman."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 121-123)
    "淡棕色皮毛的马人和有着栗色瞳孔的鸟人，[l]还有，娇小的三色猫种的猫人。"

# game/day 12.rpy:958
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_ab8637fb:

    # "Are they friends of Kouya's?"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 125)
    "或许是，洸哉认识的人吧。"

# game/day 12.rpy:962
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_34904c3f:

    # horse "「Good grief, what's this about leaving me behind?{p} Don't you trust me?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 129-130)
    horse "「真是的，就这样把我们扔下了是什么意思啊？[l]真是难以置信啊？」"

# game/day 12.rpy:966
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_27aded6a:

    # bird "「Isn't that because you're making things difficult,\n Keisuke?{w} You were all, {nw}"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 134-136)
    bird "「因为佳辅总喜欢抱怨。[l]整个院子里都是你那[鳥井 普 どっきり][wt]『真的要上去吗？』[wait time=\"500\"][鳥井 呆れ normal][wt]的抱怨的声音。」"

# game/day 12.rpy:968
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_b002b3c2:

    # extend "『Show me around!』{w=.5}\n {nw}"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 135)
    extend "整个院子里都是你那[鳥井 普 どっきり][wt]『真的要上去吗？』[wait time=\"500\"][鳥井 呆れ normal][wt]的"

# game/day 12.rpy:970
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_7d36dc0a:

    # extend " and then you go, 『We're seriously going up?』」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 135-136)
    extend "整个院子里都是你那[鳥井 普 どっきり][wt]『真的要上去吗？』[wait time=\"500\"][鳥井 呆れ normal][wt]的抱怨的声音。」"

# game/day 12.rpy:971
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_2df76d96:

    # bird "「As for the 『left behind』 thing,{w} it wasn't that far.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 139)
    bird "「所以把你丢下了。[l]也不是什么大不了的事情嘛。」"

# game/day 12.rpy:973
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_e2959ad2:

    # cat "「...」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 142)
    cat "「……」"

# game/day 12.rpy:974
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_97dbabb3:

    # "From the voices, it seems all the complaining\ncame from the horse.{w} How do I put this...\nhe seems like a unique kind of guy."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 144-146)
    "从声音上来判断，之前的抱怨好像来自那个马人。[l]怎么说呢，是个给人独特感觉的人。"

# game/day 12.rpy:978
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_15342428:

    # horse "「I dunno about that.{p} You need a bigger heart to accept me.{p} Things won't work if you can't,{w=.2} seriously.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 150-152)
    horse "「那种事情我才不知道。[l]如果不用更宽广的心胸来接受我的话。[l]事情就变得严重了，[wdt]我认真的。」"

# game/day 12.rpy:982
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_62b83122:

    # bird "「So,{w=.2} Kouya.\n Who is the person next to you?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 156-157)
    bird "「那么，[wdt]洸哉。[l]在你旁边的那人是谁啊？」"

# game/day 12.rpy:992
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_34afed7d:

    # ka "「He's a childhood friend.{p} He changed schools a while back,\n but he's come back to hang out,{w=.2} for now.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 168-170)
    ka "「我的青梅竹马。[l]以前转校后搬离这里，这个暑假回到这里来玩。」"

# game/day 12.rpy:996
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_572db6dd:

    # bird "「Ahh,{w=.2} did you mention him the other day?{p} Hmm,{w=.2} what was that name...?{w=.2}\n I remember asking about it...」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 174-176)
    bird "「啊啊，[wdt]就是你之前说的？[l]嗯，[wdt]叫什么名字呢，[wdt]确实有听过的啊，我想一下……」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1000
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_1aab15ea:

    # cat "「...[fn], [ln].」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 180)
    cat "「……西村、博行」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1004
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_66f42054:

    # bird "「Yes yes, that's it.{p} So you're [fn] [ln]-kun then...」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 184-185)
    bird "「对对，没错。[l]这样啊，你就是西村博行啊……」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1008
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_0e06cb88:

    # horse "「Seriously!?{p} The rumored [fn] [ln]!?{p} That's like the biggest scoop ever!」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 189-190)
    horse "「真的假的！？[l]　就是那个西村博行！？[l]这可是头条新闻啊！」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1009
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_a041b87b:

    # fn "「No, well, I am [fn] [ln]...」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 193)
    fn "「呃，的确是我没错，西村博行……」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1010
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_ec978cc1:

    # "All of their eyes were on me,\nfilled with immense interest or curiosity."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 195-196)
    "三个人津津有味地打量着我，简直像要用视线给我洗澡一样。"

# game/day 12.rpy:1011
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_559cd48b:

    # "It's a little... Actually, it's really embarrassing.{p}The way things are, that is."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 198)
    "等等，这样子，很尴尬啊。[l]这个情况。"

# game/day 12.rpy:1012
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_5a334043:

    # "When he noticed my discomfort,\nthe birdman looked taken aback, and said,"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 200-201)
    "似乎是注意到了我的尴尬，鸟人突然浮现出了那样的表情。"

# game/day 12.rpy:1016
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_1abe651a:

    # bird "「...Oh, sorry. Didn't mean to stare like that.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 205)
    bird "「――那个，不好意思啊，这样子盯着你看。」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1020
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_1925e141:

    # bird "「Just a while ago, Kouya was talking about you for\n a bit, and when he was talking he seemed happy.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 209-210)
    bird "「在这之前啊，有稍微听洸哉提过你啊，在讲到你的时候洸哉真的是很高兴呢。[l]"

# game/day 12.rpy:1021
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_f3abe5de:

    # bird "「I got interested,\n wondering what kind of person you were.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 211)
    bird "所以对你还挺感兴趣的。」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1022
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_eeb941cc:

    # fn "「Hwuh? Is that true?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 214)
    fn "「咦，真的是这样吗？」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1023
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_c4298e30:

    # "I blurted out in a shaky voice, surprised.{p}Even for me, I thought I sounded weird."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 216-217)
    "突然着了魔一样，那样的话就从我的嘴里自然地说出来。[l]连自己都就觉得自然地有些病态。"

# game/day 12.rpy:1027
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_dbe35894:

    # ka "「...Hey, Yuuki, don't go on so much about it.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 222)
    ka "「……喂有季，别随便讲出那样的话啊。」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1031
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_32df4926:

    # horse "「What are you saying?{w} Your tail was wagging\n when you were talking earlier.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 226-227)
    horse "「什么嘛。[l]你那时候明明是边摇着尾巴边说呢。」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1035
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_1fd75f52:

    # ka "「Wha-!?{p} There's no way that's-」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 232-233)
    ka "「呃！？[l]那是因为――」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1039
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_033d9e45:

    # bird "「No no, he's for real this time.{p} For Keisuke, that's pretty serious.{p} Wait, you weren't self-aware at the time?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 237-239)
    bird "「呀呀，这真是。[l]该说连佳辅都注意到了真是少见。[l]还是该说本人没有自觉呢？」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1043
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_0dc18e6e:

    # horse "「Yeah yeah.{p} It really is serious.{p} Right, Jun!?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 243-245)
    horse "「是啊是啊。[l]真的是很难得啊。[l]是吧，闰？」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1044
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_e2959ad2_1:

    # cat "「...」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 248)
    cat "「……」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1045
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_16ee5390:

    # "The birdman added in his agreement, double checking\nthat the catman nodded at the horseman's words."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 250-251)
    "鸟人的附和加上马人的话语，猫人只好为难地点了点头。"

# game/day 12.rpy:1046
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_f54f7fb3:

    # "For his part, Kouya looked away from my eyes\nand hung his head in silence.{w} Well actually,\nit's more like there's nothing else he could do."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 253-255)
    "这时候的洸哉，避开我的视线低下头选择沉默。[l]或者说，除了沉默他也没什么其他事可做了。"

# game/day 12.rpy:1047
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_fcde5bf8:

    # "I'm really happy about it,\nbut being blabbed about like this makes me\nfeel bad for him. I'm feeling awkward myself."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 257-259)
    "虽然听到那个很高兴，不过在本人面前暴露出来确实是很尴尬，我也注意到了这点。"

# game/day 12.rpy:1048
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_8ac9c0d6:

    # fn "「B-{w=.2}by the way, Kouya.{p} Would you mind introducing everyone...?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 262-264)
    fn "「话、[wdt]话说回来，洸哉。[l]如果能为我介绍一下大家就很感激了……」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1049
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_e1b6a9a4:

    # "Because I felt so bad for him, I tried changing\nthe subject.{w} Yes, that's nice, me.{p}Keep it up, me."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 266-268)
    "因为尴尬的气氛，还是稍微转换一下话题吧。[l]嗯，我做得不错啊。[l]我要加油啊。"

# game/day 12.rpy:1053
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_c661f341:

    # ka "「Y-{w=.2}yeah...{p} All these guys are my true friends and bandmates.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 272-273)
    ka "「啊、[wdt]嗯。[l]他们是我现在加入的乐团的伙伴。」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1060
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_e3c55533:

    # ka "「The horseman is the drummer, Keisuke.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 283)
    ka "「马人是鼓手佳辅。」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1061
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_90b0f29c:

    # ke "「Nice to meet ya!」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 286)
    ke "「请多指教！」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1068
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_aff7b4cd:

    # ka "「The birdman over there is the vocalist, Yuuki.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 296)
    ka "「那边的鸟人是，主唱有季。」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1069
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_3a225c66:

    # yu "「Nice to meet you.{w} I hope we get along.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 299)
    yu "「初次见面。[l]请多指教」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1076
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_20eaef1a:

    # ka "And, the quiet catman over there\n is the bassist, Jun.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 309)
    ka "「然后那个无口的猫人是负责贝斯的闰。」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1080
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_4bfb75ee:

    # jn "「...」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 313)
    jn "「……」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1085
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_e207655e:

    # ka "「Well, anyway,{w} we normally borrow a studio in Kazenari\n and practice there,{w} but there's some construction\n going on, so we can't use it for the time being.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 324-326)
    ka "「啊，那个，[l]平时都是借用风鸣町的工作室来做乐团的练习，[l]不过现在正在做修补工程所以不能使用。」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1089
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_6b731071:

    # ka "「We tried looking for a new place,\n but there isn't any place as good in Kazenari.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 330-331)
    ka "「为了寻找代替的地方才来这边，不过果然是没有像风鸣町那样好的地方。」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1093
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_122ab883:

    # ka "「So now we're looking around here,\n and these guys said they wanted to look around\n the village, so I'm showing them around.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 335-337)
    ka "「所以就顺便来这里看看，因为这些家伙说要在村里看看，我就给他们做向导了。」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1094
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_872d6f7d:

    # "Kouya was talking a lot faster than usual.{p}Moreover, his cheeks have slackened a bit.{p}He must really be in a hurry."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 339-341)
    "用着比平时要快的语气说着。[l]洸哉的脸颊有些紧绷。[l]果然还是，对于刚才是话题感到焦躁呢。"

# game/day 12.rpy:1095
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_c8fd6367:

    # fn "「Huh, I see then.{p} Is there a place where you can\n practice here in Minasato Village?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 344-346)
    fn "「哦，这样啊。[l]可是，水乡村这里有可以让乐团练习的地方吗？」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1099
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_6ecd4f87:

    # ka "「I was thinking of borrowing the school gym.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 351)
    ka "「是有考虑要借用学校的体育馆。」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1100
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_a27dfb6c:

    # "I see, I get it now.{p}The gym should be fine for their equipment."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 353-355)
    "原来如此，我很理解。[l]体育馆的话，在那里确实是很方便器材搬运什么的。"

# game/day 12.rpy:1104
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_ae0e0235:

    # ka "「We went and talked with Botan-sensei about it,\n and he said he was fine with it,{p} but he also told us to check with Uncle Shigure.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 359-361)
    ka "「所以就去跟牡丹老师讲了，学校方面是对此事没什么意见，[l]就姑且去跟时雨爷爷讲一下这件事情。」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1105
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_554dc6be:

    # ka "「Visiting him is fine and all, but he's out.{p} It doesn't seem like he'll be back until tonight,\n so we just packed up and went around sightseeing.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 364-366)
    ka "「去找爷爷的时候他正好不在。[l]要到傍晚才会回来，在那之前就四处走走更仔细地看看这里。」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1106
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_56275dfd:

    # fn "「I see.{w} So that's what you meant by \"guide\".」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 369-370)
    fn "「原来是这样啊。[l]那『向导』是怎么回事？」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1110
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_9b6f4333:

    # ka "「That's how it is.{p} But there's not much special about the village,\n and with nowhere to go, I'm a bit stumped.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 374-376)
    ka "「就只是那样而已啊。[l]因为水乡村除了自然风景以外什么都没有啊，要说带去哪里实在是很困扰啊。」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1114
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_94d78256:

    # ka "「On top of that, the one who suggested the\n sightseeing is spazzing out about it.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 380)
    ka "「此外，最先说要观光的那个人居然开始发牢骚。」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1124
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_055d8264:

    # ke "「Hey, I wasn't spazzing out about it.{p} I just said that climbing stairs is a pain.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 393-394)
    ke "「我哪里有在发牢骚啊？[l]只是再说要爬阶梯很麻烦而已。」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1125
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_8a21b9a1:

    # yu "「Wouldn't the world in general refer to that as\n 'spazzing out'?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 398)
    yu "「我们一般所说的『发牢骚』不就是指这个吗？」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1126
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_4bfb75ee_1:

    # jn "「...」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 401)
    jn "「……」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1130
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_0359af3b:

    # ke "「No it's not.{w} It's totally not.{p} {nw}"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 405-407)
    ke "「不是。[l]绝对不是。[l][平馬 困惑 normal][wt]应该跟大家知道的意思是不同的。不同的哦。[l]嗯。[l]不是就是不是啊。」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1132
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_6ae922ed:

    # extend "I don't really get it, but it shouldn't be.\n It's not.{w} Yeah.{w} If it's not, it's not.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 407)
    extend "不同的哦。[l]嗯。[l]不是就是不是啊。」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1136
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_733d4d71:

    # yu "「Ahh, yes yes,{w=.2} we get it,{w=.2} we get it.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 411)
    yu "「啊，是是[wdt]我知道了[wdt]我知道了」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1137
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_3be6662f:

    # "Yuuki-san spoke in exasperation."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 413)
    "有季已经懒得反驳了。"

# game/day 12.rpy:1138
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_18df79b5:

    # "Somehow, this seems like a small-time comedy act,\nbut this back and forth is pretty fun.{p}These two make such a good team."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 415-417)
    "不知道为什么，就像在看一个2人的小剧场一样十分有趣。[l]说真的，是很好的组合啊。"

# game/day 12.rpy:1142
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_7bf7b5ee:

    # ke "「If you get it, then that's fine.{p} {nw}"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 421)
    ke "「很高兴你能明白。[l][平馬 喜ぶ normal][wt]"

# game/day 12.rpy:1144
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_420a0dec:

    # extend "Now, we've been here for ages,\n so let's go to the next place.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 422-423)
    extend "那么，一直待在这里也没什么事做，差不多要去下个地方了吧？」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1148
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_b6b29aa8:

    # ke "「Oh,{w=.2} yeah.{w} If you want, [fn] do y-\n {nw}"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 427)
    ke "「啊，[wdt]对了。[l]要不然博行也[平馬 普 normal][wt]"

# game/day 12.rpy:1150
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_a884d6fa:

    # extend "...Wait,{w=.2} is it okay if I call you by first name?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 428)
    extend "――那个，[wdt]我可以直接称呼你的名字吗？」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1151
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_9f260c76:

    # fn "「Eh?{w} Oh, yes.{w} I don't mind at all.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 431)
    fn "「诶？[l]　嗯，可以。[l]完全没问题。」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1155
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_c952a844:

    # ke "「Thanks.{w} So, you wanna tag along?{p} Might be saying too much,\n but you look like you're free.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 435-437)
    ke "「谢啦。[l]那博行要不要跟着我们一起来呢？[l]说起来有点抱歉，不过你看起来挺闲的啊。」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1159
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_5c7ae60b:

    # yu "「Oh,{w=.2} that's a nice idea, Keisuke.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 441)
    yu "「嗯，[wdt]佳辅的提议不错啊。」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1163
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_6283b76c:

    # ke "「I know, right?{w} It's cool if you want\n to really pile on the praise.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 445)
    ke "「对吧？[l]　那再多称赞我一些吧？」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1167
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_9dbe0b5d:

    # yu "「Even if it was a joke,\n it was a bit cool even if you got all excited.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 449-450)
    yu "「开什么玩笑，那样的话你马上就会得意忘形的。」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1171
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_1b2728fe:

    # ke "「Leave it!{w} Leave it there!{p} {nw}"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 454)
    ke "「别管那个！[l]　别管那个啦！[l][平馬 笑 normal][wt]"

# game/day 12.rpy:1173
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_e7283d34:

    # extend "...And [fn], you don't need to be polite with\n us.{w} It sucks when everyone's all formal.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 455-456)
    extend "……还有博行，对我就不用使用敬语啦。[l]大家都那么认真的话很辛苦的。[l]更加随性一点好啦。」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1174
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_648028fb:

    # ke "「Just go with whatever works.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 456)
    ke "那么认真的话很辛苦的。[l]更加随性一点好啦。」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1175
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_a9f1be10:

    # fn "「Yes...{w=.2}I mean, yeah.{p} Okay. I'll do that.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 459-460)
    fn "「是的……[wdt]啊不对，嗯。[l]知道了，那就这样吧。」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1179
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_582b7653:

    # ke "「Yeah, just like that.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 464)
    ke "「对对，就是这种感觉。」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1183
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_19086ace:

    # yu "「...So, back on topic, what will you do,\n [fn]-kun?{w} Just like Keisuke said earlier,\n do you want to come with us?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 468-469)
    yu "「――那，话说回来，你觉得怎么样博行？[l]就像刚才佳辅说的，你能来的话那真是太好了。[l]"

# game/day 12.rpy:1184
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_77c0cf2a:

    # yu "「Kouya would probably be happy if you did.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 470)
    yu "洸哉也会很高兴的。」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1188
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_ad7d9341:

    # ka "「Why you...」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 474)
    ka "「你这家伙……」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1189
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_9a3d6ae9:

    # "Glancing at Kouya, that didn't seem likely.\nHe looked liked he'd get mad.{p}Since my heart's beating so fast, it's troubling."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 476-478)
    "向洸哉的方向瞥了一眼，看到了一个从未见过的，害羞一样的表情。[l]结果自己也不知道为什么心跳加速了，真让人为难。"

# game/day 12.rpy:1193
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_ff86718d:

    # yu "「Well,{w=.2} shall we?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 482)
    yu "「呐，[wdt]去吗？」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1194
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_ec542f20:

    # fn "「U-{w=.2}uhh...」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 485)
    fn "「那、[wdt]那个……」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1195
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_8eb3666a:

    # "Well, I am free, and I don't have a reason to refuse,\nbut what should I do?"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 487-488)
    "确实是很闲啦，也没有什么特别的理由拒绝，怎么办才好呢？"

# game/day 12.rpy:1209
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_go_a40e0084:

    # fn "「...Sure, I'll come.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 509)
    fn "「……那我就接受你们的好意一起去吧。」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1215
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_go_99399403:

    # ke "「Ohh, you said it, [fn]!」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 513)
    ke "「哦，博行那么说了！」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1221
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_go_8f20d734:

    # "Keisuke slapped me on the back\nwith a smile across his whole face."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 516-517)
    "满面的笑容浮现出来，佳辅边说边拍着我的背。"

# game/day 12.rpy:1222
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_go_e0df7148:

    # "He's probably holding back,\nbut it still hurt a bit.{p}Actually, it seems to be getting worse!"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 519-521)
    "肯定已经手下留情了吧，不过还是有点痛。[l]说起来，为什么感觉越来越用力了啊！"

# game/day 12.rpy:1231
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_go_70e9517d:

    # "Crap,{w=.2} ow!?{p}Where'd the gentleness from earlier go!?"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 524-525)
    "啊，[wdt]好痛！？[l]最开始那个和善的人跑到哪去了！？"

# game/day 12.rpy:1238
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_go_5fc6fa20:

    # ka "「Hey, Keisuke, you're hitting him too hard.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 534)
    ka "「喂，拍得太用力了吧，佳辅。」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1239
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_go_1f4b3aee:

    # "Maybe he could tell, as Kouya chided\nKeisuke-san before he hit hard enough to kill.\nSeriously nice save there, Kouya."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 536-538)
    "是察觉到我的处境了吗，在被致命一击打中之前，洸哉出声斥责了佳辅。做得真是好啊洸哉。"

# game/day 12.rpy:1243
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_go_9e23b91b:

    # ke "「Oh, for real?{w} Whoops.{p} Sorry about that [fn].」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 542-543)
    ke "「啊，真的吗？[l]　失礼了啊。[l]抱歉博行。」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1244
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_go_93e59a93:

    # "Keisuke-san stopped that movement, saving me\nfrom being beaten on like a drum.\nI dug out a deep relieving sigh."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 545-547)
    "佳辅停止了动作，我终于从被打鼓一样连打的处境中解放出来。[l]松了一口气。[l]真是危险啊，骨头和其他地方都是。"

# game/day 12.rpy:1245
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_go_ebf74df5:

    # "It was dangerous for a minute there.\nAll the way to my bones."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 547)
    "松了一口气。[l]真是危险啊，骨头和其他地方都是。"

# game/day 12.rpy:1246
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_go_3618bca5:

    # fn "「No, I'm all right.{p} Though I'd be happy if you treated me\n more gently from now on...」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 550-552)
    fn "「不，我没事啦。[l]不过如果你稍微温柔一点的话我会更高兴的……」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1250
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_go_002f1fe6:

    # ke "「Roger!{p} I'll keep that in mah mind!」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 556-557)
    ke "「收到！[l]我会记得更小心点的。」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1251
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_go_0e49b0db:

    # "...Somehow, I'm not reassured."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 559)
    "……怎么，有一种不安的感觉。"

# game/day 12.rpy:1255
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_go_13f3e236:

    # ke "「That aside, we should celebrate the\n addition to our little travel pack,\n maybe with an offering, but...」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 563-564)
    ke "「嘛，先不管那个啦，为了庆祝有新的旅途伙伴，难得的机会投一下香油钱吧……」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1259
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_go_9ba18c57:

    # ke "As he pulled out his wallet, Keisuke-san's\n expression hardened a bit. And with a quiet *clink*,\n he put it back in his pocket."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 567-568)
    ke "这么说着佳辅拿出了钱包，愣了一下。[l]然后又安静地合上钱包，塞回自己的口袋里。"

# game/day 12.rpy:1263
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_go_b2583e52:

    # ke "「...I only have a 500 yen coin, so we'll\n have to pass.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 572)
    ke "「……没有500元的硬币了，今天就算了吧。」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1267
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_go_13825aa6:

    # ka "「...Keisuke, you really do muck up everything.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 577)
    ka "「……佳辅，你这样的家伙真是让人受不了啊。」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1268
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_go_e10eb46a:

    # "No objections there.{p}I'm sure everyone else there thought the same thing."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 579-580)
    "没有异议。[l]在这个场合大家肯定都是这么想的。"

# game/day 12.rpy:1280
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_pass_c91991c3:

    # fn "「...it's been a while, but I'll pass this time.{p} It's for the band members and no one else,\n so I figure it'd be weird for me to come along.」"
