    ke "「等一下啦，不要把我扔在这里！」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1434
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_continue_97739ed7:

    # "「He's at it again,」{w=.2} the three of them thought\nas they quickly walked away and ignored him."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 850-851)
    "「又开始了」，[wdt]差点把这句话说出来的3人决定无视佳辅先走。"

# game/day 12.rpy:1435
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_continue_2c1daef1:

    # "I also followed them right as they left,{w=.2}\nand the voice behind me grew louder.{p}My cheeks were unexpectedly loose."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 853-855)
    "我也跟着他们走掉，[wdt]背后响起了那样的声音。[l]让人不由自主地脸颊放松。"

# game/day 12.rpy:1436
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_continue_7c3d952b:

    # "Lake Shiratsuyu is pretty close to the shrine.{p}If you follow the road in front of you\nthen cross the river,{w=.2} you should be pretty close."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 857-859)
    "白露湖距离神社相当的近。[l]沿着眼前的道路一直走，[wdt]穿过河流后再走一点，就能看到湖畔了。"

# game/day 12.rpy:1437
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_continue_c86b2145:

    # "It should take about five minutes.{p}Maybe I should bring up a topic in here.{p}So, what should I talk about?"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 863-865)
    "时间也就花费5分多钟。[l]在这期间我说点什么话题来活跃气氛吧。[l]那么，说点什么呢？"

# game/day 12.rpy:1456
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_you_106ccd1a:

    # fn "「Say, how did everyone come to meet each other?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 894)
    fn "「说起来，大家是怎么认识的呢？」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1457
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_you_905db496:

    # "I wanted to know a bit more about everyone,{w=.2}\nso I began with that."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 896-897)
    "机会难得，想稍微了解一下大家的事情，[wdt]所以那样提出了问题。"

# game/day 12.rpy:1458
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_you_27ea19d2:

    # "I'm sure they aren't from Minasato, and I was\nthinking that they were from neighboring towns,{w} but\nI was a bit interested in how Kouya got to know them."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 899-901)
    "他们毫无疑问不是水乡村的居民，应该是住在临近的镇子把，[l]对洸哉是怎么和他们认识的有点感兴趣。"

# game/day 12.rpy:1459
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_you_3534bee1:

    # "...No,{w=.2} no matter which way I put it,\nwhat Kouya did in the time I've been gone\nis what I'm really interested in."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 903-905)
    "……不，[wdt]不如说，我对自己不在的这段时间里洸哉在做什么[wdt]这件事更在意一些。"

# game/day 12.rpy:1463
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_you_e3f19991:

    # ke "「Ah,{w=.2} that's right...{p} {nw}"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 910-911)
    ke "「啊，[wdt]说起来啊……[l][平馬 普 normal][wt]一开始，是我和洸哉吧？[l]"

# game/day 12.rpy:1465
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_you_4872c69b:

    # extend "In the beginning, wasn't it just me and Kouya?{p} We met at that pops's place.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 912)
    extend "在大叔的那里见了面。」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1466
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_you_c592db79:

    # ka "Yep.{w} Jun and Yuuki joined in sometime later on.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 915-916)
    ka "「说的是呢。[l]在那之后不久闰和有季才加入的。」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1467
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_you_e07c32bd:

    # fn "「Who's 'Pops'?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 919)
    fn "「『大叔』是啥？」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1468
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_you_c82c9d3e:

    # yu "「The manager of the musical instruments store\n Kouya works at.{w} Even now he takes care of us\n in a lot of ways. He's a really nice person.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 922-923)
    yu "「洸哉打工的乐器店的店长啦。[l]帮我们解决了很多的麻烦，[wdt]是个很好的人。」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1469
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_you_9d949288:

    # ke "「It was a long time ago,{w=.2} but when I first thought\n of starting up a band and looking for members,\n Kouya was the one he introduced me to first.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 926-928)
    ke "「已经是几年前的事了，[wdt]在我最初组建乐团寻找团员的时候，大叔第一个介绍的人就是洸哉了。」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1473
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_you_f99a0cad:

    # ke "「Then after that, we talked about random crap\n until we clicked with one another,{w=.2}\n then started out as a team.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 933-935)
    ke "「然后在见面之后，在谈话中觉得彼此都很中意，[wdt]于是就决定马上组合了。」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1474
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_you_34785a68:

    # ke "「...Or something like that.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 941-942)
    ke "「那是什么让人误解的说法啊，不过大致上就是那样了。[l][洸哉 普 normal][wt]我觉得这个家伙挺有趣的，[wdt]"

# game/day 12.rpy:1478
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_you_af8be9a9:

    # ka "「That sounds wrong in all sorts of ways,\n but that's basically how it went.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 942-943)
    ka "不过大致上就是那样了。[l][洸哉 普 normal][wt]我觉得这个家伙挺有趣的，[wdt]手臂看起来也不错。」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1482
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_you_543437b2:

    # ka "「Well, I thought he was amusing,{w=.2}\n and he seemed to be legit.\n I was also looking for people to team up with.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 946-947)
    ka "「原本我也是在找志同道合的伙伴。[l]现在想起来，[wdt]真的是很巧啊。」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1486
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_you_ef42c855:

    # ke "「Honestly, it's all right to say 'it turned to love,'{w=.2}\n you know?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 952)
    ke "「你就坦白地说「我喜欢你」[wdt]不好吗？」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1487
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_you_eed0e0db:

    # ka "「And,{w=.2} since just a guitar and drums wasn't going\n to cut it, and because I wanted to make a band,{w=.2}\n I went looking for other members.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 957-959)
    ka "「但是，[wdt]果然只有吉他和鼓手是不行的，于是就带着原本的组建乐团的目的，[wdt]开始寻找其他的成员。」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1491
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_you_c7f56286:

    # ke "「...You tsundere.{w=.2} I understand.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 964)
    ke "「……这是傲娇，[wdt]我明白的。」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1492
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_you_11552e51:

    # ka "「I thought about taking an ad out in a magazine,{w=.2}\n but the manager went and did the work for us."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 967-969)
    ka "「本来还想在出版的杂志上登找人的广告的，[wdt]不过受到店长的照顾。[l]介绍给我们两个店里的常客，闰和有季。」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1493
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_you_acb1c5e2:

    # ka "「Jun and Yuuki were amongst the regulars\n he introduced to us.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 969)
    ka "介绍给我们两个店里的常客，闰和有季。」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1494
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_you_da5e2d2f:

    # fn "「Huh.{w=.2} So everyone is a regular at the same shop.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 972)
    fn "「诶，[wdt]那大家都是同一家店的常客啊。」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1495
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_you_f4371b0e:

    # ka "「Yeah,{w=.2} so from the beginning I could\n at least remember everyone's faces.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 975-976)
    ka "「啊，[wdt]所以从一开始大家都对彼此的脸有印象。」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1496
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_you_bc0bc722:

    # ka "「Because of that, things went quickly,{w=.2}\n and about two weeks later,\n Yuuki was the last one to join up.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 979-980)
    ka "「因为这样进展很快，[wdt]不到2周的时间最后的有季也决定加入我们的乐团了。」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1500
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_you_5fdae564:

    # ke "「Yeah,{w=.2} that was pretty fast, wasn't it?{w=.2}」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 985)
    ke "「啊，[wdt]马上就决定了不是吗？」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1501
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_you_df39236d:

    # yu "「Yep,{w=.2} I decided to join almost right away.{p} {nw}"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 988-989)
    yu "「嗯，[wdt]我大体上是立即就决定要加入了呢。[l][鳥井 笑 normal][wt]感觉如果和那个成员一起的话，可以做出许多事，"

# game/day 12.rpy:1503
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_you_140fc3f8:

    # extend "I felt that if he was a member, then he could do so\n many things. It was like instinct.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 990)
    extend "该怎么说呢，就是直觉吧。」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1507
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_you_9bf6a79f:

    # jn "「I thought so too.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 995)
    jn "「我也是这么觉得的。」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1508
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_you_c4661b2f:

    # fn "「Were you surprised?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 998)
    fn "「没有被吓一跳吗？」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1512
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_you_51e56ff3:

    # yu "「That might be a bit too long ago, you know?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 1003)
    yu "「这不是有点久之前的事了么？」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1513
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_you_57cf156b:

    # "Yuuki-san became a bit embarrassed\nfrom being put into the spotlight."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 1005-1006)
    "有季说着，觉得有点不好意思。[l]于是为了掩饰笑了笑，[wdt]然后大家都笑了出来。"

# game/day 12.rpy:1514
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_you_35b8fe64:

    # "He laughed like he was trying to hide it,{w=.2}\nand we laughed along with him."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 1006)
    "于是为了掩饰笑了笑，[wdt]然后大家都笑了出来。"

# game/day 12.rpy:1518
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_you_8adc7ea7:

    # yu "「But I think it was like that.{p} Something like a seed of fate.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 1011-1012)
    yu "「但是我认为这种感觉。[l]就是命运的安排吧。」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1519
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_you_f42444f9:

    # fn "「So from a bunch of friends from a store,{w=.2}\n you all came together as a group, huh.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 1015)
    fn "「在同一间相识，[wdt]然后加入了同一个乐团了呢。」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1523
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_you_dca07858:

    # ka "「That's right.{p} Someway or another we settled into things.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 1021-1022)
    ka "「说的是呢。[l]嘛，[wdt]经历了这样和那样的事，就变成现在这个样子了。」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1524
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_you_c2809845:

    # fn "「I see then.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 1025)
    fn "「原来如此。」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1525
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_you_687c2c1e:

    # "I see,{w=.2} so Kouya works part-time at a music store.{p}There's probably no better place for him,\nsince he likes music so much."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 1027-1029)
    "这样啊，[wdt]洸哉在乐器店打工。[l]也就是说，对于喜欢音乐的人没有比这更好的打工场所了。"

# game/day 12.rpy:1526
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_you_01f82901:

    # "On top of that, he's made real friends like this.{p}There doesn't seem to be room for any more,{w=.2}\nbut even I could tell they were all nice people."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 1031-1033)
    "此外，还能遇到这样的同伴。[l]虽然才认识没多久，[wdt]但是大家都是好人这点我却十分清楚。"

# game/day 12.rpy:1527
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_you_d749c894:

    # "As I thought,{w=.2} everyone's changed a lot\nsince I've been gone."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 1035-1036)
    "果然，在我不在的这段时间里，[wdt]大家都发生了各种各样的变化啊。"

# game/day 12.rpy:1528
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_you_02d87038:

    # ke "「Oh, is that it?{w} Lake Shiratsuyu?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 1039)
    ke "「哦，难道说那个就是吗？[l]　白露湖」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1529
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_you_7a5646fb:

    # "I was being caught up in my own world,{w=.2}\nuntil Keisuke-san's words brought me back to Earth."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 1041-1042)
    "沉浸在自己的世界里发出奇怪感慨的我，[wdt]被佳辅所说的话拉回现实。"

# game/day 12.rpy:1530
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_you_5ac8bfb3:

    # "Looking at where he was pointing,{w=.2}\nI saw the shining surface of the water\nreflecting the summer sunlight."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 1044-1046)
    "视线朝着他手指的方向移动，[wdt]可以看到那边是因为反射夏天的日光而闪闪发亮的水面。"

# game/day 12.rpy:1541
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_me_8218b3ca:

    # "Hmm,{w=.2} I'm a little stumped for things to talk about."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 1059)
    "唔，[wdt]但是对这个话题感到有点为难啊。"

# game/day 12.rpy:1542
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_me_490fcf12:

    # "...Well, there was that one thing from earlier."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 1061)
    "没办法了，虽然是刚才自己避开的话题，不过……"

# game/day 12.rpy:1550
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_me_b742b2c6:

    # fn "「By the way,{w=.2} you guys said that Kouya\n was talking about me to you all,\n but what did he talk about?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 1075-1076)
    fn "「对了，[wdt]刚才有说道洸哉说了一些关于我的事情，到底说了些什么呢？」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1551
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_me_4f511578:

    # "Yes, I'll be honest.{p}I'm totally interested in that!"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 1078-1079)
    "是的，直接地说了出来。[l]因为真的是很在意啊！"

# game/day 12.rpy:1552
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_me_02cabbad:

    # "After all, \"that\" Kouya was\nwagging his tail as he was talking about me.{p}I'd have to be crazy to not be intrigued by it!"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 1081-1083)
    "因为那个可是让洸哉一边摇着尾巴一边说的话啊。[l]怎么可能不让人在意啊！"

# game/day 12.rpy:1556
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_me_5765a0f1:

    # ka "「Hey, [fn] that's-」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 1089)
    ka "「喂，博行，那个是――」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1566
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_me_ac1f6902:

    # ke "「You wanna hear?{p} You do, dontcha!?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 1098)
    ke "「想知道吗？[l]　果然还是想知道对吧！？」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1567
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_me_82525324:

    # fn "「Y-{w=.2}yeah...」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 1101)
    fn "「嗯、[wdt]嗯……」"

