    # extend "Stuff that's there{w=.2} and stuff that's not, any-{p} {nw}"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 1114)
    extend "真的事假的事，[wdt]全部都――[l][平馬 困惑 ジャンプ][wt]痛痛痛痛痛！？」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1579
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_me_c50b317a:

    # extend "Gaaah!?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 1114)
    extend "真的事假的事，[wdt]全部都――[l][平馬 困惑 ジャンプ][wt]痛痛痛痛痛！？」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1583
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_me_d8bf7c1b:

    # yu "「Your face is too close, can you back off a little?{p} No one wants to see your face from that close.{p} Sorry, [fn]-kun.{w} I'll get rid of this ass.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 1119-1121)
    yu "「你的脸太近了啦，稍微离远一点吧？[l]没有人想要从那么近的距离看你的脸啦。[l]抱歉，博行。[l]现在就把这个障碍物拿开。」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1593
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_me_112fe2a8:

    # ke "「Hey, ow!{w} I get it,{w=.2}\n I get it, so stop pulling my tail, will ya!?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 1127-1128)
    ke "「等下，好痛！[l]我知道了，[wdt]我知道了所以不要拉我的尾巴啊！？」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1599
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_me_1ed71de3:

    # "As if being dragged along (I think he is, actually){w=.2}\nKeisuke-san moved back{w=.2}\nto a more normal distance away."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 1133-1135)
    "由于被拖的缘故（我认为实际上大概是被拖了）[wdt]佳辅退后了一些，[wdt]恢复和我平时的距离。"

# game/day 12.rpy:1600
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_me_7eacdfb4:

    # "His eyes have some tears in them,\nand it's a little pitiful to see."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 1137)
    "眼中似乎泛着几滴泪光，看起来十分痛的样子。"

# game/day 12.rpy:1604
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_me_540c95d1:

    # yu "「Good grief,{w=.2} you get so excited sometimes,\n Keisuke...」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 1142)
    yu "「真是的，[wdt]佳辅总是立刻就得意忘形……」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1605
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_me_bd3c1d05:

    # ke "「Whaaaat?{p} Don't get all jealous of me getting close\n to [fn] so fast.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 1145-1146)
    ke "「什么嘛。[l]我这么快就接近博行让你感到嫉妒了吗？」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1606
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_me_029a5b31:

    # yu "「Yes yes, whatever you say.{p} {nw}"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 1149)
    yu "「啊，是啦是啦我知道我知道了啦。[l][鳥井 普 normal][wt]"

# game/day 12.rpy:1608
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_me_8f049410:

    # extend "Keep talking already.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 1150)
    extend "继续刚才的话题吧。」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1614
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_me_5d94ee68:

    # ke "「Aye aye, sir!{p} {nw}"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 1157)
    ke "「Yes Sir！[l][平馬 喜ぶ目開け normal][wt]"

# game/day 12.rpy:1616
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_me_9983c023:

    # extend "Now then,{w=.2} you were asking about\n what Kouya was talking about?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 1158)
    extend "那，[wdt]真想知道洸哉说了什么来着？」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1617
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_me_6da38fb5:

    # "Putting on a smile that said\n「doesn't matter to me, if we keep talking,」\nKeisuke-san double checked with me."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 1160-1162)
    "浮现出的笑脸似乎在说着，[wdt]「你真的想知道那也没办法」，佳辅再一次地确认着。"

# game/day 12.rpy:1618
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_me_36cab9b2:

    # "I nodded immediately in response."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 1164)
    "我点了点头作为回答。"

# game/day 12.rpy:1619
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_me_5fc6ea42:

    # "I knew Kouya was making a face as if he wanted\nto say something,{w=.2} but for now I chose to not\nlook at him.{w} I'll apologize now.{w=.2} Sorry Kouya."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 1166-1168)
    "洸哉用一副想说什么的表情望着我们，[wdt]我们则是装作没有看见。[l]先在这里道歉了。[wdt]对不起，洸哉。"

# game/day 12.rpy:1623
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_me_59efb6b7:

    # ke "「Uh-huh...{p} How do I put this...{p} He was in a super good mood.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 1173-1174)
    ke "「是嘛……[l]更确切地说，他简直是兴高采烈啊。」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1624
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_me_686dfdb1:

    # ke "「I don't know the right expression for it,\n but it's something like that.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 1177-1178)
    ke "「我不知道该怎么说比较好，[wt]不过就是那种感觉。」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1625
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_me_29d6ac81:

    # fn "「A super good mood?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 1181)
    fn "「兴高采烈？」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1626
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_me_da5313c3:

    # ke "「Yeah.{w} I've seen him every day these few years,\n but I've never seen him like that before.{p} Right,{w=.2} Yuuki? Jun?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 1184-1186)
    ke "「啊。[l]在这几年里虽然每天都会和洸哉见面，但是从来没有见过那样的洸哉呢。[l]呐，[wdt]有季、闰？」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1627
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_me_78da2d54:

    # yu "「Yep.{w} He'd been cheerful since that morning.\n When I asked him about it,{w=.2}\n he said a friend from grade school came back.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 1189-1191)
    yu "「说的是呢。[l]那天从早上起来就很高兴，当我问发生了什么的时候，[wdt]他说小学时候的朋友要回来，边说边散发着幸福的光环呢。」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1628
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_me_b5a2801b:

    # yu "「He was putting out this happy aura for a while.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 1191)
    yu "回来，边说边散发着幸福的光环呢。」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1632
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_me_7ec609b7:

    # jn "「His tail wagged a lot, too.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 1196)
    jn "「尾巴也，摇来摇去的。」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1636
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_me_ccf611f0:

    # yu "「Yeah, that's right.{w=.2} Always swishing back and forth,\n left and right.{w} If I had to compare the atmosphere\n around him to something...」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 1201-1203)
    yu "「对对。[wdt]一直摆来摆去的。[l]那个时候洸哉周围的气氛表现率，[wdt]至少是闰的5倍啊，5倍！」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1637
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_me_7a95eb5f:

    # yu "「I'd say he was about five times\n happier than Jun. Yeah, five times.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 1202-1203)
    yu "那个时候洸哉周围的气氛表现率，[wdt]至少是闰的5倍啊，5倍！」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1638
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_me_22d1b6ec:

    # "Keisuke-san and Jun-kun both nodded at this."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 1205)
    "嗯嗯，[wdt]佳辅和闰都赞同地点了点头。"

# game/day 12.rpy:1639
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_me_ddfad4d7:

    # "I wonder what's up with that method of comparison.{p}Well, I do kinda get it,{w=.2}\nbut I feel like it's some kind of in-joke."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 1207-1209)
    "说起来，那个『气氛表现率』是什么鬼啦。[l]虽然不是很明白，[wdt]但是那个指标似乎是作为大家共同认知的一个东西。"

# game/day 12.rpy:1640
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_me_6515caf9:

    # "As for that five times thing,{w=.2} it sounds like\nsomething relatively impossible between them.{p}The way they nod their heads gives that impression."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 1211-1213)
    "还有那个5倍的数值，[wdt]似乎是一个普通人无法达到的水平。[l]从其他人点头这点就可以感觉到这件事。"

# game/day 12.rpy:1644
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_me_f0b4d45d:

    # "From a quick glance at Kouya,{w=.2}\nhis brow was wrinkled into a sullen expression\nthat screamed \"I don't want to hear any more.\""
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 1217-1219)
    "瞥了一眼洸哉的样子，[wdt]「我不想再听这个话题了」几乎要脱口而出了，眉头紧皱着一副苦涩的表情。"

# game/day 12.rpy:1645
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_me_074900c1:

    # "I'll apologize again.{w=.2} Sorry, Kouya."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 1221)
    "我第二次道歉。[wdt]对不起，洸哉。"

# game/day 12.rpy:1649
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_me_e4483dee:

    # ke "「It's kinda scary.{p} I was afraid that someone messed with him{w=.2}\n and left him for dead that day.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 1226-1228)
    ke "「说起来还有点恐怖。[l]对那天的洸哉做什么事情他都没有追究，[wdt]还在担心会不会突然被他杀了呢。」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1650
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_me_7a2dcc72:

    # ke "「I'm so glad you're alive.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 1231)
    ke "「现在还能活着真是太好了。」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1654
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_me_10141670:

    # yu "「Was it just for August?{w} Ever since you came back\n [fn]-kun, it feels like every day is different.{p} It calms down for several minutes though.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 1236-1237)
    yu "「是在8月初吗？[l]　博行回来的时候，每天的气氛都不一样呢。[l]某种意义上来说是稍微冷静了下来。」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1655
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_me_0b1e72a0:

    # fn "「Ehh?{w} No, I suspect it's more of the opposite.{p} You're not making that up, are you?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 1240-1241)
    fn "「咦？[l]　不，那个部分是不是反了。[l]很奇怪啊？」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1659
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_me_031d6234:

    # "「Nope, not at all.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 1249)
    "「不、完全不会。」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1663
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_me_79deb749:

    # "I was denied in complete synchronity.{p}I think I noticed Jun-kun's voice in there too,{w=.2}\nso he must think so too."
