# game/day 12.rpy:1667
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_me_971317ea:

    # "I looked aside at Kouya again,{w=.2}\nhe's gone straight past sullenness\nand gradually into complete emptiness."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 1259-1261)
    "再一次斜视着洸哉，[wdt]洸哉的表情由可怕慢慢地回复到正常。"

# game/day 12.rpy:1668
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_me_54b3a1f1:

    # "For Kouya, there probably isn't anything\neven more embarrassing.{w} I wouldn't ever want\nto be stuck in the same situation."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 1263-1265)
    "对洸哉来说，这种事情会感到不好意思也是正常的。[l]我也绝对不想要处在他那种立场。[l]……不过自己却是这样话题的发起者。"

# game/day 12.rpy:1669
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_me_0957ab21:

    # "Then again,{w=.2} I was the one who started this..."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 1265)
    "……不过自己却是这样话题的发起者。"

# game/day 12.rpy:1670
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_me_c67f61d2:

    # "But I think I understand Kouya a bit better.{p}He looked forward to meeting with me again.{p}And he was honestly happy."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 1267-1269)
    "不过对洸哉的心情我也多少能理解。[l]对于他期望与自己重逢的心情。[l]还有他坦率的高兴。"

# game/day 12.rpy:1671
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_me_3d02a00f:

    # "So this time I'll use different words.{p}And this time it won't be in my head,\nI'll give them to him with my voice."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 1271-1273)
    "所以这一次要用不同的词汇。[l]这一次不是藏在心中，而是用声音传达给洸哉。"

# game/day 12.rpy:1672
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_me_095fe7ec:

    # fn "「Thanks, Kouya.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 1276)
    fn "「谢谢你，洸哉。」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1676
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_me_e53a7c79:

    # "Kouya's eyes opened in confusion at my words,{p}{nw}"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 1280)
    "洸哉听了我的话，稍稍有点吃惊，眼睛睁得大大的，[l][洸哉 普 normal][wt]"

# game/day 12.rpy:1678
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_me_e95cb7e1:

    # extend "but they quickly returned to normal."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 1281)
    extend "但是马上又回复了平时的样子。"

# game/day 12.rpy:1679
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_me_54685671:

    # ka "「Nah,{w=.2} it's nothing you need to thank me for.{w=.2}」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 1284)
    ka "「没什么，[wdt]别因为他们跟你说这些事情就道谢啊。」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1680
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_me_f1961216:

    # fn "「Huh?{w=.2} But it really fits in this case.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 1287)
    fn "「诶，[wdt]但是在这种场合不是很适合这么说吗？」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1681
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_me_4820f1c7:

    # ka "「Really?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 1290)
    ka "「是吗？」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1682
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_me_bdc69e5b:

    # fn "「Yeah.{p} I'm so glad, so just accept it.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 1293-1294)
    fn "「是啊。[l]我也很高兴啊，所以你就接受那句话吧。」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1686
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_me_4d2391f8:

    # ka "「...You sure?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 1300)
    ka "「……是吗？」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1687
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_me_8074338a:

    # fn "「Yeah.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 1303)
    fn "「就是这样。」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1691
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_me_53ceec48:

    # ke "「Umm... Sorry to intrude while you two\n are in your own little world, but...」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 1308-1309)
    ke "「那个……[l]虽然打扰你们的二人世界很不好意思啦……」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1695
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_me_98b29722:

    # "Our two-man loop came to a sudden stop.{p}To be honest,{w=.2} I'm a little glad it did."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 1314-1315)
    "终于打断了两个人已经进入循环的对话。[l]说真的，[wdt]我松了一口气。"

# game/day 12.rpy:1699
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_me_35da3c69:

    # ke "「Is that Lake Shiratsuyu?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 1320)
    ke "「难道说，[wdt]那个就是白露湖吗？」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1700
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_me_5ac8bfb3:

    # "Looking at where he was pointing,{w=.2}\nI saw the shining surface of the water\nreflecting the summer sunlight."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 1322-1324)
    "视线朝着佳辅手指的方向移动，[wdt]可以看到那边是因为反射夏天的日光而闪闪发亮的水面。"

# game/day 12.rpy:1722
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_lake_e8f5ff10:

    # "If you look after getting close to the water,{w=.2}\nyou'd notice that the water's perfectly clear\nand that you could see all the way to the bottom."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 1353-1355)
    "如果站在靠近湖畔的地方看，[wdt]可以发现湖水非常地通透，可以十分简单地看到水底。"

# game/day 12.rpy:1723
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_lake_c91c9a65:

    # "Lake Shiratsuyu,{w=.2} located in Minasato Village.\nOne of the most important places."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 1357-1362)
    "白露湖，[wdt]也是在水乡村里的一个重要的地方。因为有不知道多么古老的时候龙神就一直居住在里面，[wdt]这样流传着的传说存在。[l]洸哉现在对我们说明着。"

# game/day 12.rpy:1724
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_lake_01f27a5b:

    # "A dragon god that lived here from ancient times,{w=.2}\nseems to be the reason why it's so important,{p}Kouya explained."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 1360-1362)
    "因为有不知道多么古老的时候龙神就一直居住在里面，[wdt]这样流传着的传说存在。[l]洸哉现在对我们说明着。"

# game/day 12.rpy:1725
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_lake_144ebbe5:

    # ke "「Ahh, when you put it like that...{p} {nw}"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 1365-1366)
    ke "「啊，这么说起来……[l][平馬 喜ぶ normal][wt]好、[wdt]好像挺有气氛的嘛！」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1727
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_lake_cefb9348:

    # extend "I-{w=.2}it has such an awesome mood here!」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 1366)
    extend "好、[wdt]好像挺有气氛的嘛！」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1731
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_lake_9ac0fd49:

    # yu "「I don't really feel like\n coming up with some sort of punchline...{p} I won't force myself if I can't think of anything.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 1371-1373)
    yu "「虽然对你那多余且草率的评论都懒得吐槽了，但是……[l]什么想法都没有的话，不说话不是比较好吗？」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1735
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_lake_c20d3cd3:

    # ke "「Well, that can't be helped.{p} I don't see it as a normal lake,{w=.2}\n but I think it's best that way.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 1378-1380)
    ke "「这是没办法的嘛。[l]都已经看到湖了啊，[wdt]还是说些什么比较好吧，一般都会这么想嘛。」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1736
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_lake_2ba8da82:

    # ke "「That's how it feels,{w=.2} to me anyway.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 1383)
    ke "「我就是[wdt]有这样的使命感啊！」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1737
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_lake_19a50376:

    # yu "「Ah, I see...」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 1386)
    yu "「啊，所以……」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1741
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_lake_7094b6a1:

    # jn "「But,{w=.2} it's a beautiful place.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 1391)
    jn "「不过，[wdt]这里很漂亮。」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1745
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_lake_0742c4a6:

    # yu "「Yep, sure is.{w} A place that a god lives in,{w=.2}\n and a place treasured by the villagers.\n I think I can understand that.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 1396-1398)
    yu "「嗯，的确是这样。[l]可以理解有神住在这里[wdt]或是对村子很重要这样的事呢。」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1746
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_lake_05f25711:

    # ka "「Well, when we were kids this was a place\n we might have damned ourselves while playing around.{p} I think we liked it here.{w} Right, [fn]?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 1401-1403)
    ka "「嗯，在我们小时候，虽然这么做不太好不过我们是把这里当成一个游乐场的，[l]还挺喜欢这里的。[l]对吧，[wdt]博行？」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1747
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_lake_a6be1138:

    # fn "「Uh-huh.{w} Now that you mention it,{w=.2}\n we probably did defile the place,\n when I think about it...」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 1406-1407)
    fn "「嗯，是的。[l]说起来，[wdt]现在想起来的确是件不好的事情啊……」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1751
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_lake_80eb78ec:

    # ke "「Won't the god forgive them as mistakes\n of little kids?{w} He lives in a lake this huge,\n so his heart must be just as big, right?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 1412-1414)
    ke "「小时候做错的事情神会原谅的吧？[l]住在这么广阔的湖中的话，[wdt]心胸也应该很宽大不是吗？」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1755
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_lake_3d405d0e:

    # ka "「...Maybe.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 1420)
    ka "「……说得是呢。」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1756
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_lake_5053a7be:

    # "He probably has so many things he wants to say,{w=.2}\nbut Kouya swallowed them all up and kept them inside.{p}I mean,{w=.2} he's making such a cool face right now."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 1422-1424)
    "大概是原本有很多想要说的事情吧，[wdt]不过洸哉把到嘴边的话又咽了下去。[l]嗯，[wdt]露出了一副苦涩的表情。"

# game/day 12.rpy:1757
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_lake_f27dd5d7:

    # "But that lasted for only a moment,\nafter which he went back to his usual look."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 1426-1428)
    "但是那也只出现了一瞬，接下来马上就回复成平常的表情了。[l]我似乎听到了他切换到「嘛，算了」模式的开关的声音。"

# game/day 12.rpy:1758
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_lake_d948997a:

    # "I feel like I can hear him switching over to\n\"Well, whatever then\" mode."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 1427-1428)
    "我似乎听到了他切换到「嘛，算了」模式的开关的声音。"

# game/day 12.rpy:1762
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_lake_735d170a:

    # ka "「Oh yeah, [fn].{w=.2}\n You said that there was something here\n that worried you, but what exactly is it?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 1434-1436)
    ka "「对了博行，[wdt]你之前说这里有令你在意的东西，那是什么东西呢？」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1763
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_lake_12bfbadf:

    # fn "「Hm... How do I put this, it feels like a curse...{p} ...Back then, I have a memory of making a secret\n base somewhere here.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 1439-1441)
    fn "「呃，怎么说呢，应该说是遭到报应了吗，[l]……有着以前在这里的深处做了一个秘密基地的记忆，[wdt]然后对它现在怎么样了很在意。」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1764
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_lake_c547c3cd:

    # fn "「I was thinking about what happened to it.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 1441)
    fn "记忆，[wdt]然后对它现在怎么样了很在意。」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1765
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_lake_56ac8ea2:

    # "It's possible that it might still be around,\njust where I left it.\nI had that hope within my chest."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 1443-1444)
    "说不定，[wdt]它会像以前一样就那么留在那里，胸中产生了这样一种期待。"

# game/day 12.rpy:1766
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_lake_1817b45d:

    # "It doesn't matter much to me what state it's in,{w=.2}\nbut since we're here, I wanted to check up on it."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 1446-1447)
    "虽然对那里留下了多少也无所谓啦，[wdt]但是既然来到了这里，多少都想去确认一下。"

# game/day 12.rpy:1770
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_lake_4f9c3ed7:

    # yu "「Ohoh, a secret base.{p} Niiice, I wanted to make one too.{p} It seemed like so much fun.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 1452-1454)
    yu "「诶，秘密基地啊。[l]真好啊，我也一直想做一个呢。[l]总觉得很有趣啊。」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1774
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_lake_7154c44c:

    # ke "「A secret base is a man's passion.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 1459)
    ke "「男人的浪漫就是秘密基地呢。[l]我也常常想，"

# game/day 12.rpy:1775
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_lake_482b7ad1:

    # ke "「I used to think, 'I wanna make one, too'{w=.2}\n but in the end I got too old for it.{p} So, where did you make this base?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 1459-1461)
    ke "「男人的浪漫就是秘密基地呢。[l]我也常常想，自己要做一个出来，[wdt]结果已经过了做这个事的年龄了。[l]那么，那个基地做在哪里了呢？」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1776
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_lake_144d2971:

    # fn "「In a thicket over there.{w=.2} It's pretty complex\n and it took me half of a summer to build,{p} but it should be around here, I think...」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 1464-1466)
    fn "「在对面繁茂草木的深处，[wdt]还挺复杂的呢，花了半个夏天做的，[l]是这样对吧？」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1780
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_lake_488f7ea4:

    # ka "「That's right, you did make one.{p} ...Yeah,{w=.2} it was around here.{p} You really remembered, [fn].」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 1472-1474)
    ka "「说起来的确是做过的啊，那样子的。[l]――啊，[wdt]确实是在这里。[l]真亏你还能记得博行。」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1781
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_lake_1fb9c689:

    # "「Seriously,」 I thought to myself.{w} That said,\nmost of my memories have faded since I left,{w=.2}\nso why do I remember this?"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 1476-1478)
    "的确，自己也这么觉得。[l]大部分的记忆，都随着离开这里以后渐渐地变得稀薄了，[wdt]为什么还记得这件事呢。"

# game/day 12.rpy:1782
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_lake_0b94866c:

    # fn "「Yeah...{w} Just like you said, it was fun, Yuuki-san.{p} That part of my memory was probably strong.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 1481-1482)
    fn "「啊……[l]正如有季所说的，因为很高兴啊。[l]所以这部分的记忆特别强。」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1783
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_lake_c94dae2a:

    # "For now, I should complete it myself."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 1484)
    "总而言之，如所说那样地做了自我总结。"

# game/day 12.rpy:1784
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_lake_f32e8d9d:

    # ka "「Huuuh.{p} Well, how about we go take a look at it?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 1487-1488)
    ka "「哼。[l]那总而言之去看看吧。」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1789
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_lake_fe3c7af3:

    # "With that,{w=.2} everyone paired off\nand went into the grove of trees.{p}I'm sure it would look strange to most others."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 1494-1496)
    "以此为契机，[wdt]大家一个接一个地闯入杂木林中。[l]如果有别人看到的话，大概会发出异样的眼神吧。"

# game/day 12.rpy:1790
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_lake_ae27be58:

    # "Based on my memories and Kouya's,{w=.2} we made our way\nthrough the filtered sunlight beneath the leaves,{w=.2}\nand before long we reached our destination."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 1498-1500)
    "凭借着我和洸哉的记忆，[wdt]当通过了洒满叶间透过阳光的小路后，[wdt]终于好不容易到达了。"

# game/day 12.rpy:1791
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_lake_86b8d73d:

    # "A small, shoddy secret base,{w=.2}\ncobbled together with scraps\nfrom Tatsu-nii's place and a towering tree."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 1502-1503)
    "在参天的大树下，[wdt]是用由辰兄一点一点收集的废弃木材所组成的，[wdt]小小的，拙劣的秘密基地。"

# game/day 12.rpy:1792
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_lake_12ed5778:

    # "Our base that could deal with the rain fairly well,{w=.2}\nusing torn blue sheets that we got from\nhere and there and fixed together for a roof."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 1505-1507)
    "使用从各处搜集而来的破旧蓝色板材，修补在一起当作屋顶，[wdt]作为对应下雨的方法的我们的基地。"

# game/day 12.rpy:1793
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_lake_dfb2e0f7:

    # "When we finished at the time it looked relatively\nsteady,{w=.2} but it's very worn-out from years of neglect."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 1509-1511)
    "完成的时候看起来还是挺坚固的，[wdt]是多年弃之不顾的原因吗，已经变得破破烂烂的了。"

# game/day 12.rpy:1794
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_lake_1c7c0108:

    # "The scrap wood parts are rotting,{w=.2} and the blue\nsheets could no longer function as before,{w=.2} so I could\ntell that the inside was a huge mess from outside."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 1513-1515)
    "废材的一部分已经腐化了，[wdt]蓝色的板材也已经失去了原有的作用，[wdt]基地里面的惨淡状况大概已经从外面就可以了解了。"

# game/day 12.rpy:1802
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_lake_d88c63fc:

    # ka "「There was a base here,{w=.2} once.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 1529)
    ka "「基地还在呢，[wdt]姑且。」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1803
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_lake_38def90e:

    # fn "「Yeah,{w=.2} it looks terrible now...」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 1532)
    fn "「嗯，[wdt]不过样子看起来很严重啊……」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1804
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_lake_f4cf6ce6:

    # "When looking at it all ruined like this,{w=.2}\nthe conversation also felt that way."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 1534-1536)
    "一行人排成一横列看着这样的状况，[wdt]会话也自然的是这种感觉。[l]怎么说呢，大家都很微妙地，难以进行评论。"

# game/day 12.rpy:1805
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_lake_44ed1aeb:

    # ke "「But, since you said you made it as a kid,{w=.2}\n it held up surprisingly okay.{p} I still see it now, since it left its form behind.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 1539-1541)
    ke "「不过，从小孩子制作的角度来说，[wdt]这个已经很坚固了。[l]现在即使是通过残留的样子也能姑且看出原来的形状。」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1806
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_lake_a694e964:

    # ka "「Probably because the materials weren't that bad.{p} The leftover wood at Tatsuki-san's place, remember.{w=.2}\n he let us use it for this.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 1544-1546)
    ka "「因为材料本来就不错。[l]木头都是辰树那里用剩下来的，[wdt]他拿来给我们使用。」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1807
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_lake_2bfe6404:

    # fn "「Tatsu-nii's place was always a carpenter's home.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 1549)
    fn "「从很早以前辰兄那里就是木匠屋呢。」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1808
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_lake_558d893c:

    # ka "「Weren't they temple builders?{p} Well,{w=.2} leaving the materials alone\n for a few years turns it into this.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 1552-1553)
    ka "「正确地来说应该是修建神社寺院宫殿的木匠吗？[l]不过，[wdt]即使是好的材料经过几年的放置也会变成这样。」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1809
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_lake_d2fe0b1e:

    # yu "「But someone left it here without taking it down.{p} Is this an okay place to put it?{w} For a secret base.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 1556-1557)
    yu "「不过至今为止都留下来了没有被人破坏掉，[l]不是说明制作的场所很好吗？[l]　作为秘密基地来说。」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1810
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_lake_5a9454e0:

    # ka "「Still, I wonder who it was.{w=.2}\n The one who decided to make the secret base here.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 1560-1561)
    ka "「是啊，倒是是谁呢，[wdt]第一个说要在这个地方做秘密基地的？」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1811
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_lake_b661bbc6:

    # fn "「Huh, wasn't it you?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 1564)
    fn "「咦，不是洸哉吗？」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1815
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_lake_134908fe:

    # ka "「...You kidding?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 1570)
    ka "「……不会吧？」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1816
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_lake_2ce1e03f:

    # "「Stop playing around,」 his rising brow seemed to say.{p}Sorry,{w=.2} but I'm not playing around here..."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 1572-1573)
    "洸哉皱着眉头似乎要说「别开玩笑了」。[l]但是很遗憾，[wdt]这并不是开玩笑啊……"

# game/day 12.rpy:1817
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_lake_3b18859d:

    # fn "「No, I'm serious.{p} When we were all deciding where to build it,{w=.2}\n you were the one who said to make it here.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 1576-1578)
    fn "「不，是真的。[l]在大家讨论要在什么地方作的时候，[wdt]洸哉提出了这个地方。」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1818
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_lake_98be81c2:

    # ka "「Seriously?{p} ...No,{w=.2} I don't remember that at all.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 1581-1582)
    ka "「很的吗？[l]……不是吧，[wdt]我完全没有印象啊。」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1819
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_lake_68dcc50a:

    # fn "「I'm sure of it.{w=.2} I got the feeling\n you said something amazingly original.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 1585-1587)
    fn "「确实是这样。[wdt]还说了觉得这个地方很厉害。[l]像是离水边很近啦，村里很少人会来所以不用担心被发现啦之类的。」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1820
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_lake_41729e2a:

    # fn "「It's good to have it near water,\n and it's a good place to hide it, since\n people from the village don't come here often.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 1585-1587)
    fn "「确实是这样。[wdt]还说了觉得这个地方很厉害。[l]像是离水边很近啦，村里很少人会来所以不用担心被发现啦之类的。」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1821
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_lake_a45db679:

    # ka "「...Even for me,{w=.2} how do I say it, I'm amazed.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 1590)
    ka "「……即使是我，[wdt]该怎么说呢，也觉得很吃惊啊。」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1822
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_lake_d9c8c328:

    # "As he briskly scratched his head,{w=.2} Kouya faced\nthe base and looked at it one more time."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 1592-1593)
    "挠了挠头，[wdt]洸哉再一次，向基地的方向望去。"

# game/day 12.rpy:1826
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_lake_b9ff0882:

    # "In those eyes,{w=.2} I'm sure he's\nseeing a lot of his old memories.{p}...Because lately, that's the way it is for me."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 1597-1599)
    "在那眼里，[wdt]一定浮现出久远的记忆，与现在所见的景象重合。[l]……因为我最近，也是这样。"

# game/day 12.rpy:1827
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_lake_36ef310b:

    # ka "「...Should we make one?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 1602)
    ka "「……做一个吗？」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1831
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_lake_1e5bd7e9:

    # fn "「Eh?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 1607)
    fn "「诶？」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1832
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_lake_aeb9c1bb:

    # "I wonder when Kouya did that.{w} It's a distant\nfeeling, but I think it was after several blinks.{p}All of a sudden, Kouya opened his mouth."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 1609-1611)
    "从洸哉变成那个样子后过了多久呢。[l]感觉很长，但是大概其实只有几次眨眼的时间吧。[l]洸哉突然开口那样说了。"

# game/day 12.rpy:1833
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_lake_13fcf42f:

    # "It was too sudden,{w=.2} as I couldn't grasp\nthe meaning of his words."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 1613-1614)
    "实在是很唐突，[wdt]所以我没能很好地领会那句话的意思。"

# game/day 12.rpy:1837
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_lake_1df019cc:

    # ka "「I said 'should we make one.'{w} A secret base.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 1619)
    ka "「所以说，再来做一个吧。[l]秘密基地。」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1838
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_lake_9eb82979:

    # fn "「...Eh,{w=.2} right now?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 1622)
    fn "「……诶，[wdt]现在吗？」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1839
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_lake_31ff766c:

    # "When I finally got it,{w=.2} I was so\ntaken aback by it that I didn't hear anything else."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 1624-1625)
    "终于理解那个真正的意思，[wdt]不过由于过于惊讶我没听到别的事情。"

# game/day 12.rpy:1843
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_lake_b8e09388:

    # ka "「No,{w=.2} it'd be impossible right now, but sometime.{p} This summer, next year, or maybe sometime after that.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 1631-1633)
    ka "「不，[wdt]现在就做出来实在是不可能，总有一天。[l]这个夏天，或者是明年，[wdt]又或者是那之后，但是……」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1844
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_lake_3087b57b:

    # ka "「I thought maybe it'd be fun,\n to make one again someday.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 1636)
    ka "「总有一天，[wdt]再来做一次的话一定很有趣吧。」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1848
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_lake_7e9b79b7:

    # ke "「Really!?{w} Me too!{w} I wanna do it too!」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 1641)
    ke "「真的吗！？[l]　我也要！[l]　我也要参加！」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1852
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_lake_73b53ac4:

    # yu "「Ah,{w=.2} I want to do it too then!」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 1646)
    yu "「啊，[wdt]那我也要参加！」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1856
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_lake_04b8e8b6:

    # jn "「Me three.{w=.2} I want to try.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 1651)
    jn "「我也，[wdt]要参加。」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1860
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_lake_61dad8be:

    # ka "「Yeah,{w=.2} let's invite all the guys\n from the village, and make a huge one.{p} It's like we're joining a secret society.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 1657-1659)
    ka "「嗯，[wdt]那把村子里的那群家伙一起叫来，做一个大的吧。[l]弄一个像秘密结社那样的。」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1861
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_lake_badebca1:

    # "Oh, as I thought-"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 1661)
    "啊，果然――"

# game/day 12.rpy:1862
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_lake_9710e915:

    # ka "「Hey, {w=.2}[fn].{p} You're in too, aren't you?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 1664-1665)
    ka "「呐，[wdt]博行。[l]你也参加吗？」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1863
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_lake_8e048f1f:

    # fn "「...Of course I am.{p} There's no way I won't!」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 1668-1669)
    fn "「――那还用说吗。[l]怎么可能不参加呢！」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1864
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_lake_375113b2:

    # "Just as I thought, Kouya will always be Kouya."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 1671)
    "果然，不管怎样洸哉就是洸哉。"

# game/day 12.rpy:1865
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_lake_4a5ee5ec:

    # "For a second I saw Kouya laughing like he did\nas a kid,{w=.2} and it felt so nostalgic."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 1673-1674)
    "看着有点像少年的时候一样笑着的洸哉，[wdt]总觉得有种十分怀念，却又很新鲜的感觉，[l]"

# game/day 12.rpy:1866
translate chinese_simplified kouya12_lake_90f5509a:

    # "But now, I feel a fresh new feeling,{p}a feeling that's embarrassing,{p}but also very happy."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_05.ks (KS 1673-1675)
    "看着有点像少年的时候一样笑着的洸哉，[wdt]总觉得有种十分怀念，却又很新鲜的感觉，[l]有点难为情的，但又令人高兴的感觉。"

# game/day 12.rpy:1885
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki12_d4b40f3b:

    # tp "「[fn], you can put that here.{p} You don't haveta use the tools, so it's okay to\n drop 'em.」"
    tp "「[博行]，把这里收拾好。[l]别的东西不用管了，放在那儿吧。」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1886
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki12_9de8008a:

    # fn "「Yes, sir. ｣"
    fn "「明白了。」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1890
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki12_34563cad:

    # tp "「Now then, it's time we finish up here.{p} It's all wood shavings, so burning it will be fine.{p} Let's burn the office trash, while we're at it.」"
    tp "好了，快点收拾干净吧。[l]因为全是木屑，拿到焚化炉烧掉就行了吧。[l]顺便把事务所里的垃圾也一起丢掉吧。"

# game/day 12.rpy:1891
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki12_9c9ae5f9:

    # fn "「Well, that's easy enough.{p} After this... there's nothing left, right?」"
    fn "「好了大致上弄干净了。[l]接着要干的事是……呃，没事了啊。」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1895
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki12_4c83a98d:

    # ta "「Yo, [fn]. What'cha you doing over here?」"
    ta "「嘿，[博行]。在这种地方干什么呢？」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1896
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki12_b93d7e51:

    # "Tatsu-nii came in, shaking his tail\nin a good mood.{w} Spotting me from\nacross the room, he came over."
    "在终于打扫完之后，看着已经干净的房间发呆的时候[l]辰兄摇晃着尾巴，看起来心情很好似的，[l]朝[咱]的方向走过来了。"

# game/day 12.rpy:1897
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki12_16b851c2:

    # fn "「Cleaning up, as you can see.{p} You just don't learn, do you?\n You'll make him mad again.」"
    fn "「怎么看都是在打扫吧。[l]辰兄还真是罚不怕啊，被辰平叔看到又要挨骂了哦。」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1901
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki12_38f52034:

    # ta "「Heh, it's not like I came over to play.{p} Just picking up some tools, is all.」"
    ta "「哼，我又不是来玩的啦。[l]我可是特意来这里取东西的。[l]因为接下来该处理木材了，所以要用到锛子。」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1902
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki12_ffeb8206:

    # ta "「After this I'll be cleaning some wood,\n so I'll need the butterfly plane.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_m_03.ks (KS 44)
    ta "因为接下来该处理木材了，所以要用到锛子。」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1903
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki12_ead0d8ea:

    # fn "「That one, huh? Your toolbox is over... there,\n Tatsu-nii.{w} Here, I'll get it for you.{p} This is for unrefined lumber, right?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_m_03.ks (KS 50-52)
    fn "「锛子啊。那个，辰兄的工具箱我记得是在……啊，在这儿了。给。这是把木头粗糙的地方刨平用的工具吧？」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1904
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki12_4e167a05:

    # "I took out the small tool from the bag,\nand gave it to Tatsu-nii."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_m_03.ks (KS 55)
    "递给了辰兄。"

# game/day 12.rpy:1908
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki12_9fe094e6:

    # ta "「Thanks. You know a lot now, huh?{p} Someone must have taught you without telling me.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_m_03.ks (KS 59-60)
    ta "「谢啦，知道得很详细嘛。是谁在俺不知道的情况下告诉你的？」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1909
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki12_02fe9c8e:

    # fn "「I've been working here for how long, now?\n I should at least know this much.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_m_03.ks (KS 63-64)
    fn "「[咱]也已经干过好几天的活了诶，这点程度已经是常识啦。」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1913
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki12_48b8e9f3:

    # ta "「Gahaha, for a guy who's never worked in carpentry,\n you sure are talking big.{p} Anyway, Tetsu-san taught you that, didn't he?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_m_03.ks (KS 68-69)
    ta "「噶哈哈，连现场都没去过的小家伙说什么呢。肯定也是哲先生教给你的吧。」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1914
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki12_c3d2db17:

    # fn "「Yep, that's right.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_m_03.ks (KS 72)
    fn "「没错。"

# game/day 12.rpy:1915
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki12_276f5289:

    # fn "「He politely explained a bunch of stuff to me, like\n what the tools are called, how the artisans have\n their own tools, and who puts what where.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_m_03.ks (KS 73-74)
    fn "工具的名称，手艺人各自使用的工具，谁把自己的工具放在哪里……这些都很详细地告诉[咱]了。」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1919
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki12_06d39043:

    # ta "「I thought as much.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_m_03.ks (KS 78)
    ta "「就知道会是这样。」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1920
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki12_fc74ed9e:

    # fn "「I remember all of it, perfectly.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_m_03.ks (KS 81)
    fn "「[咱]已经全部都记下来了哦。全部。」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1924
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki12_25f8da0e:

    # ta "「Is that so?{w} What's this one, then?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_m_03.ks (KS 85)
    ta "「真的？那就考考你~」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1925
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki12_1c56b7ee:

    # "As he said that, Tatsu-nii picked up a\ncarpentry tool.{w} Blackened with dirt,\nit looked like a miniature wooden cart."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_m_03.ks (KS 87-89)
    "辰兄说着，拿起一个大工用的工具。还是一个带着黑色污迹的、木制的、上面带着一个“车轮”的东西。"

# game/day 12.rpy:1926
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki12_71ce8be6:

    # "Let's see, that one is..."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_m_03.ks (KS 91)
    "唔唔，那个大概是……"

# game/day 12.rpy:1927
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki12_21b917ec:

    # fn "「That one's easy enough. An inking device, right?{p} It's used for drawing lines on lumber.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_m_03.ks (KS 94-95)
    fn "「这还不简单，是墨斗。在木材上画线用的东西吧。」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1931
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki12_3b35615f:

    # ta "「Right.{w} The ink is pitch black,\n so that one was easy.{p} {nw}"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_m_03.ks (KS 99)
    ta "「正确。是因为墨水太黑了，所以很容易辨认吧。[辰樹 普 normal][wt]"

# game/day 12.rpy:1933
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki12_c864cd3d:

    # extend "What about this one?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_m_03.ks (KS 100)
    extend "这样的话……这个怎样？」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1934
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki12_beb4ba25:

    # "Tatsu-nii picked up an L-shaped tool.{p}I've seen these at school."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_m_03.ks (KS 102-103)
    "这次辰兄手里拿着的是L字形弯曲的规尺。这样的东西在学校也看见过。"

# game/day 12.rpy:1935
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki12_eb250200:

    # fn "「That's a carpenter's square.\n I remember because of the ruler.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_m_03.ks (KS 106)
    fn "「是矩尺，因为属于规尺类的，所以记得很清楚。」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1939
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki12_e1391008:

    # ta "「You got it again.{p} It's mostly used for dimensioning, but lately\n a bunch of carpenters don't know how to use them.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_m_03.ks (KS 110-112)
    ta "「哦，又被你说中了……虽然这东西也能量出尺码，不过现在不会用这个的大工也挺多的。」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1940
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki12_1b013734:

    # fn "「Huh? It's not just some bent ruler?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_m_03.ks (KS 115)
    fn "「呃，不就只是个弯曲的规尺么？」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1944
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki12_a3ff0bbb:

    # ta "「Nope.{w} Using it is an art,\n it's not just a simple measuring tool.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_m_03.ks (KS 119-120)
    ta "「这就不对了~。用它可是有相应的技巧的。这可不只是个测量物体的工具哦。」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1945
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki12_87da7d0a:

    # ta "「The carpenter's square, butterfly plane, and\n the inking device.{p} You could say those are the three key tools.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_m_03.ks (KS 123-124)
    ta "「矩尺，锛子，墨斗，它们可以说是在大工的工具中，三个相当神奇的存在呐。」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1946
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki12_adb9ab6d:

    # fn "「Oh, I see, then.{p} To be able to use them makes you amazing,\n Tatsu-nii.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_m_03.ks (KS 129-130)
    fn "「唉，这样的啊。那就是说会用这些东西的辰兄也很厉害呢。」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1950
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki12_af17555b:

    # ta "「Well... I'm not that good, yet.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_m_03.ks (KS 134)
    ta "「得了……我还差得远呢。」"

# game/day 12.rpy:1951
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki12_9c7b3508:

    # "Oh yeah, he's still an apprentice.{p}Always getting scolded every day.{p}Hang in there, Tatsu-nii."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_m_03.ks (KS 136-138)
    "啊啊，也是，辰兄还只是见习呢。每天都惹辰平叔生气。加油吧，辰兄。"

# game/day 12.rpy:1956
